    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is mitigated by the strong inter-laboratory reproducibility (CV 3.2%) and the conservative nature of single-condition ASTM F1717 loading. Overall credibility is sufficient for Medium model risk and Medium decision consequence. Assessment accepted with notation of test condition limitation.",
